There are many reasons one can change one's address. Some of them involve
the loss of privileges and representational authority (say one got fired).
Thus the safest is to associate certificates with distinguished names, both
for the signer and the recipient of such certificates.

There are obviously some cases where this will cause complications, but
better safe than sorry.

David
